'''Reaper''' has a virtual [[MIDI]] keyboard you can open and use to trigger MIDI tracks and [[Software instrument]] tracks.

You can access it by going to '"View/Virtual MIDI keyboard'''




[[File:Reaper virtual MIDI keyboard menu.png]]




A virtual keyboard will then appear.




[[File:Reaper virtual MIDI keyboard.png]]



You can change the octave by making sure the '''Arrow keys change octave/channel''' option is selected. Then use the left and right arrow keys to change octaves. 


[[File:Reaper Virtual MIDI keyboard.png]]




